IP geolocation
--------------
This product includes IP geolocation data created by DB-IP (https://db-ip.com),
the "IP to Country Lite" database, downloaded from:
  https://db-ip.com/db/download/ip-to-country-lite

It is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License
(CC BY 4.0): https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

The bundled database (/usr/share/GeoIP/dbip-country-lite.mmdb) is redistributed
UNMODIFIED (the build only decompresses the published .mmdb.gz) and is used to map
peer IP addresses to country flags. The DB-IP attribution is also surfaced in the
application UI (Insight view). You may replace the database with your own MaxMind
GeoLite2-Country database via the insight.geoip_db config setting.

